</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1">Unknown mechanism:<ul id="ulist0155" class="list" style="list-style-type:none"><li id="u0260"><p id="p0460">Decreased dose may be needed</p></li></ul>
</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1">Monitor INR</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1">Remdesivir</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1">N/A</td>
<td colspan="1" rowspan="1">Potential inducer of CYP1A2, CYP2B6 and CYP3A4<br>No dose adjustment recommended</td>
